quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  63,9,"O you who believe! Let not your properties or your children divert you from the remembrance of Allah. And whosoever does that, then they are the losers"
  63,10,"And spend of that with which We have provided you before death comes to one of you, and he says: \"My Lord! If only You would give me respite for a little while, then I should give Sadaqah from my wealth, and be among the righteous"
  63,11,And Allah grants respite to none when his appointed time comes. And Allah is All-Aware of what you do